    AddBodyLocationActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for adding a body location to a record.
    AddMapLocationActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for adding a map location to a record.
    DatePickerFragment
    Description:
    Handles the creation of a DialogFragment that provides the user with a gui to set a new date on a visual calendar.
    PatientAdapter
    Description:
    Custom Array Adapter for presenting one Text Views based on provided Patients.
    PatientAddProblemActivity
    Description:
    The patient add problem screen for the Application, this presents the gui for a patient to add a new problem by setting a title, start date and a comment.
    PatientAddRecordActivity
    Description:
    The patient add record screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a patient to add a new record to one of their problems.
    PatientEnterRegisterCodeActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for a patient to enter a registration code they are given in order to register another phone.
    PatientLoginActivity
    Description:
    The patient login screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a Patient to enter their username and proceed to login, or to move to a Patient sign up screen if they don't have an account.
    PatientMenuActivity
    Description:
    The patient main menu screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for the Patient to proceed to screens in which they can add new problems, view their existing problems or search their problems.
    PatientProblemViewActivity
    Description:
    The patient problem viewing screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for the Patient to view one of their problems data, as well as the ability to proceed to screens where they can view all of the problem's attached records, add a new record to the problem or view a slideshow of all the problem's record's photos.
    PatientProfileActivity
    Description:
    The patient profile viewing screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for the patient to view their username and contact information.
    PatientRecordViewActivity
    Description:
    The patient record viewing activity screen for the Application, this presents the gui for the patient to view one of their record's data of the title of the problem that owns it, the timestamp of its creation and the user that created it.
    PatientSearchActivity
    Description:
    The patient problem searching screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for the patient to search through their problems and records utilizing keywords.
    PatientSignUpActivity
    Description:
    The patient sign up screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a new Patient to sign up by entering a username and their contact information in the form of an email and phone number.
    PatientViewProblemsActivity
    Description:
    The patient view problems screen for the Application, this presents a gui for a patient to view a list of their problems and proceed to view a given one further by clicking on them.
    PatientViewRecordsActivity
    Description:
    The patient view records screen for the Application, this presents a gui for a patient to view a list of the records attached to a problem and proceed to view a given one further by clicking on them.
    PatientViewRegisterCodeActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for viewing a registration code for the given patient which can register them on another phone.
    PhotoAdapter
    Description:
    Custom Array Adapter for presenting one with Image Views based on provided Bitmaps.
    PhotoSelectorActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for a User photo addition screen, this presents the gui for a User to view already added photos and to proceed to add further ones either by taking new ones or by choosing existing ones from their phone photo library.
    ProblemAdapter
    Description:
    Custom Array Adapter for presenting one with Text Views based on provided Problems.
    ProviderAddPatientActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider add patient screen, this presents the gui for a Provider to add a patient they are assigned via a provided register code.
    ProviderLoginActivity
    Description:
    The care provider login screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a Care Provider to enter their username and proceed to login, or to move to a provider registration screen if they don't have an account.
    ProviderMenuActivity
    Description:
    The care provider main menu screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for the Provider to proceed to screens in which they can add new patients, view their already added patients or search through their patient problems.
    ProviderPatientProfileActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for a Care Provider's patient profile viewing screen, this presents the gui for a Care Provider to view their patients contact info and to open a screen to view a list of their problems.
    ProviderPatientViewProblemsActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider patient problems list screen, this presents the gui for a Care Provider to view a list of their patients problems and proceed to a given one by clicking them.
    ProviderPatientViewRecordsActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider patient view records screen, this presents the gui for a Provider to view a list of the records attached to a problem and proceed to a given one by clicking them.
    ProviderProblemViewActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider patient problem view screen, this presents the gui for the Provider to view one of their patient's problems data, as well as the ability view all of the attached records to the problem or to view a slideshow of all the problem's records photos.
    ProviderRecordViewActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider patient record view screen, this presents the gui for the Provider to view one of their patient's records data in terms of the problem that owns it, the timestamp of its creation and the user that created it.
    ProviderRegistrationActivity
    Description:
    The care provider sign up screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a new Provider to sign up by entering a username.
    ProviderSearchActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for a Care Provider problem searching screen, this presents the gui for the Care Provider to search through their Patients problems and records using keywords.
    ProviderViewPatientsActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the Care Provider view patients screen, this presents the gui for a Provider to view a list of their patients and proceed to a given patients profile by clicking on them.
    RecordAdapter
    Description:
    Custom Array Adapter for presenting one with Text Views based on provided Records.
    SearchAdapter
    Description:
    Custom Array Adapter for presenting one with Text Views based on provided Problem results.
    SlideshowActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for a photo slideshow screen, this presents the gui for a user to view a group of photos in a slideshow format.
    StartScreenActivity
    Description:
    The starting screen activity for the Application, this presents the gui for a user to proceed to either a Patient or Care Provider login screen.
    TextEditorFragment
    Description:
    Handles the creation of a DialogFragment that provides a gui for a user to edit a piece of text.
    ViewBodyLocationActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for viewing a body location of a given record.
    ViewMapLocationActivity
    Description:
    The Activity for the view map locations screen, this presents the gui of a Mapbox map from which a user can see markers at the passed map locations.
